{"tid":934344,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[賴地硬] 山齊士：「盧卡古成日開雪櫃凍到我無態！」","createTime":"2018-12-09T08:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T09:17:28.000Z","uid":28938,"like":280,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"bbd83ff56a27072d2729555cd589a645ab1dbc67","tid":934344,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"據英國消息，山齊士在曼聯更衣室裡的坐位靠近雪櫃，有人打開雪櫃時他總會被寒氣襲擊，他對此有所抱怨。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnzqR2U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnzqR2U.png&h=7dbb67ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在球隊更衣室裡，山齊士的位置距離雪櫃最近，雪櫃為曼聯全隊提供了冷飲，每當有球員或者工作人員打開雪櫃時，智利人總會被寒氣襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n山齊士自去季起已抱怨過冰箱的位置，更特別批評盧卡古總愛賽前、半場及全場結束後取運動飲品，寒氣的襲擊令智利人「無態」及長傷不癒。<br />\n<br />\n經多次反映後，摩連奴亦關注此事，更令工作人員搬走雪櫃。對此有消息人士指出，盧卡古曾於球會訓練時公開回應：「Nonono（不不不）！條粉腸本身就係雪櫃俾人雪緊啦，關我鬼事咩！他媽的！」<br />\n<br />\n法國Nineup報記者英國報道"},{"pid":"cc419cccd19862c0c2e188f02cd99940bb7596fc","tid":934344,"uid":142351,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b07034564fa6e23af6977cd35d367c318ef0741d","tid":934344,"uid":69568,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"回晒塘。。。"},{"pid":"9b146c0d513fedae45edef09851ff332adc7cbe7","tid":934344,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"全能到開雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94700a0f7b8b5e026f8110bfc364a361a290146c","tid":934344,"uid":1977,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:06:43.000Z","msg":"唔好笑....."},{"pid":"94f04a70a2b0422d791feb877db5e53ffa82158a","tid":934344,"uid":15830,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:12:03.000Z","msg":"全盛時期仲未返黎<br />\n仲未去到M永遠排在N之前"},{"pid":"f2340d5a923361c3e2775de2248b65bab197cd76","tid":934344,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,